- cs.IR (Information Retrieval): The paper mentions the use of profile information and user-generated content for link prediction, which are common in information retrieval tasks. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of deep learning techniques for link prediction falls under the artificial intelligence subfield.
